<h1 id='mail-api'>Mail API</h1><h2 id='post-email-from-server'>POST email from server</h2><pre class="highlight json tab-json"><code><span class="p">{</span><span class="w">
    </span><span class="s2">"to"</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="s2">"jones@restdb.io"</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w">
    </span><span class="s2">"subject"</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="s2">"Trigger email from you database"</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"> 
    </span><span class="s2">"html"</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p">{</span><span class="s2">"name"</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="s2">"Jones"</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="s2">"body"</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="s2">"..."</span><span class="p">},</span><span class="w"> 
    </span><span class="s2">"company"</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="s2">"Acme Inc"</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"> 
    </span><span class="s2">"sendername"</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="s2">"Acme support"</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w">
    </span><span class="s2">"template"</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="s2">"MyTemplate"</span><span class="w">
</span><span class="p">}</span><span class="w">
</span></code></pre>
<blockquote>
<p>Will result in a JSON output like:
[
    {}, {}, {}
]</p>
</blockquote>

<p><code>POST https://{mydatabase}.restdb.io/mail</code></p>
<h3 id='request-body-options'>Request body options</h3>
<table><thead>
<tr>
<th>Option</th>
<th>Description</th>
</tr>
</thead><tbody>
<tr>
<td>to</td>
<td>One valid receiver email address</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>subject</td>
<td>Email subject text line</td>
</tr>
</tbody></table>
<h3 id='response-array'>Response array</h3>
<table><thead>
<tr>
<th>Parameter</th>
<th>Description</th>
</tr>
</thead><tbody>
<tr>
<td>body</td>
<td>Send email <a href="sendmail-options">options</a></td>
</tr>
</tbody></table>

<p>Read more <a href="https://restdb.io/docs/mail-api#restdb">about mail API here</a>.</p>
